Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:48.00,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,这次有好好地道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.54,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算什么呀 芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不找到你 就不算结束吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.14,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
