Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.92,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽…芽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…芽芽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽… 是芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见了…芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.08,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不应该叫名字的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.09,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽不擅长玩捉迷藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.46,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太 说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:21.05,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就终于可以结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜欢你了 芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也最喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢芽芽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也最喜欢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分别的时候不能只有一方说了就算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我实现了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了 芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 仁太又把芽芽弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}弄哭了～ 弄哭了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}去告老师吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}波波 你这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}弄哭了～ 弄哭了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仁太你不能这样 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吵死了波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.87,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.87,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,还想和大家待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.63,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:39.17,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我要转世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:43.89,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以…和大家在一起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:45.85,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:51.85,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,惹仁太哭了 道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.06,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预——备！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽 找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.73,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽果然还是笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们渐渐长大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着季节变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路边绽放的小花也逐渐在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个季节绽放的花 叫什么名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻摆动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像碰一下就会刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凑近闻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有淡淡的 蓝色的阳光的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那香气渐渐淡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也渐渐长大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那朵花 一定还在某处绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们不管什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要继续实现那朵花的愿望
